{"tid":2006834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藏哮喘藥當毒藥 警拖半年棄告","createTime":"2020-05-08T04:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:43:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e03d9909ec2ca4101c36531c72c813902c51fb","tid":2006834,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/7Q3Q662XWF74RHTMXBQ7VA7Y2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2F7Q3Q662XWF74RHTMXBQ7VA7Y2M%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=c249e26e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2F7Q3Q662XWF74RHTMXBQ7VA7Y2M%2F&h=f4d4db24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/7Q3Q662XWF74RHTMXBQ7VA7Y2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n藏哮喘藥當毒藥 警拖半年棄告<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870493_6639.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870493_6639.gif&h=1d6ad629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方當日截查疑運送示威物資客貨車，拘捕一名司機。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7.1衝擊立法會後，警方廣設路障，其中一名客貨車司機被捕，當中一個控罪是「管有第一部毒藥」，但原來所謂「毒藥」只是哮喘藥，警方仍然拖足半年，到兩個月前才承認證據不足而放棄提告。協助司機的立法會議員譚文豪批評警方濫捕，「唔講仲以為警方搗破咩金三角毒梟販毒大案」。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪斥濫捕<br />\n<br />\n去年7.1衝擊立法會後，警方廣設路障，四出搜捕。。。。。。。。。。。。。附近被警方截查後被拘捕，起初被控「藏有攻擊性武器」，其後又改。。。。。。。。。。。。藥」被捕，由西區警區刑事調查隊跟進，司機獲准保釋候查，須定期到。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n協助司機的立法會議員譚文豪表示，近日遇到該被。。。。。。。。。。。。據不足而放棄提告。<br />\n<br />\n司機稱終於「鬆一口氣」，但仍對當日警方的濫捕。。。。。。。。。。。。有身孕的妻子翌日到警局探視。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪指出，所謂藏有攻擊性武器及藏有第一部毒。。。。。。。。。。。案？但事實上只係鉸剪、𠝹刀、哮喘藥」。該司機指警方至今仍未歸還。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪譴責警方濫捕「老屈香港人」，又叫鄧炳強。。。。。。。。。。。。毅』嘅反黑組！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮"},{"pid":"78a5abc76a42bbf806aee96f229cbe113ba0c547","tid":2006834,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"但事實上只係鉸剪、𠝹刀、哮喘藥」。該司機指警方至今仍未歸還<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肯定dum 晒落垃圾桶，佢地都知告唔入"},{"pid":"a31b16945ff5878d52e534c8702fef3136f0cb7f","tid":2006834,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b30015e10074a3353ab2ee46a71398329dbd443","tid":2006834,"uid":19527,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"哮喘藥當毒藥<br />\n白粉就當鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1380596a2f6eef006b94707a2deaae5c2c835a3f","tid":2006834,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"濫用執法, 一陣明明冇罪都要你還押幾個月一年<br />\n真係犯罪D黑狗可以周圍走, 出半糧, 唔告, 上訴搏打甩"},{"pid":"569e1db4d8b718d85a290f5ac864e2c8ed9534ed","tid":2006834,"uid":37408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"死黑警，浪費法律資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4aea676816f11b3dd6a357badb8c2fbc4a6d43","tid":2006834,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"濫捕，濫暴無後果"},{"pid":"06e69b63cc69fa4d0800ff56458537eb664fa53f","tid":2006834,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"咁市民係咪都可以濫用投訴班狗"},{"pid":"ee219bf1571eebaad6b3e0f552180a971aae46a4","tid":2006834,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:36:49.000Z"